Site Collection
===============
. create a Wyman Document Library
. upload "treeView" folder
. upload "js" folder


UI Site
=======
Parent UI Site
. create a page "add.aspx"
. create a page "approve.aspx"
. create a page "feedback.aspx"

Child Data Site
. create a page "dashboard.aspx"
. create a page "tasks.aspx"
. create a page "process.aspx"
. create a page "implementation.aspx"
. create a page "rejection.aspx"
. create a page "complete.aspx"
. create a page "management.aspx"
. create a page "exception.aspx"

. update the "Navigation" 

Add New/Revised Spec -> /sites/wyman/eswa/SitePages/add.aspx
Open New/Revised Spec -> /sites/wyman/eswa/SitePages/dashboard.aspx
Open Implementations -> /sites/wyman/eswa/SitePages/implementation.aspx
Completed New/Revised Spec -> /sites/wyman/eswa/SitePages/complete.aspx 
Rejected New/Revised Spec -> /sites/wyman/eswa/SitePages/rejection.aspx
Open Management Escalations -> /sites/wyman/eswa/SitePages/escalations.aspx

